text: aur na unheen logon par koee ilzaam hai jo tumhaare paas aae ki tum unake lie savaaree baaham pahuncha do aur tumane kaha ki mere paas (to koee savaaree) maujood nahin ki tumako us par savaar karoon to vah log (majabooran) phir gae aur hasarat (va aphasos) use us gam mein ki un ko kharch mayassar na aaya
